history.content:
Hi All,

Last semester there were a few people who tried using CS 199 forms to get independent study units for classes that had long wait lists. Please be aware this is NOT allowed. CS 199 is intended to be used for research units where students are supervised and evaluated. Also, all CS 199 sections are P/NP and do not have letter grades.

For those interested in submitting a CS 199 form, please submit your forms before the add/drop deadline on 2/13. (Keep in mind that late add fees begin the 4th week of instruction.)

You can bring forms to Soda 379 M-F between 1-4pm for processing until 2/13/19.
